Packages:

Pandas
NLTK
Geopy
Spacy



Instructions:

The scraper needs to be called in terminal/command line:
1. Open a terminal/command at the location of the scraper 'CentralAfricanRepublicScraper'
   in your terminal run the following script

2. write: 'scrapy crawl News_Scraper -o NewsScraperReuters.csv -t csv' - this will save a csv in your file directory

           syntax: scrapy crawl SCRAPER_NAME -output FILENAME.csv -t csv

3. After the scraper is finished, run __init__.py under 'CentralAfricanRepublicScraper'
   to launch the event detection program

4. Open and run 'Event Detection - Reuters Map.ipynb' to display interactive map